doctype 5
html.all

	include header

	div.all
		div(style="background-color:#292929; border-top-left-radius:1em; border-top-right-radius:1em; padding:4px; padding-left:12px; color:white; height:22px; white-space:nowrap;")
			| Error #{error}
		
		div(style="margin:0px; font-size:16px; background-color:white; padding:10px; padding-top:20px; padding-bottom:20px;")
			| Sorry, we could not find 
			div(style="border:1px dotted black; padding:4px; padding-left:16px; margin:20px; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; border-radius:.4em;")
